title: Where they'll finish...
text:
Where they'll finish... 
Where they’ll finish... 
The men’s and women’s basketball coaches in the CIAA announced their picks to win the 2015-16 league championships. Livingstone was selected to win both titles. The Winston-Salem State women were selected to finish fifth in the league, and the men were picked to finish third.
